---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="FennaAI | Features"
  description="Discover the features of FennaAI — your private, personal AI that runs locally and learns from your data."
>
  <div class="page features-page">
    <h1>FennaAI Features</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      FennaAI is designed to give you a personal AI that’s private, powerful,
      and easy to use. Here’s what you can do:
    </p>

    <section class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Train Your AI</h2>
        <p>
          Teach FennaAI using your own documents, emails, notes, or business
          data. Your AI adapts to your needs and stays private on your machine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Work Offline</h2>
        <p>
          Once installed, FennaAI runs completely offline. No internet
          connection is needed for chatting or training your AI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Choose Your Model</h2>
        <p>
          FennaAI supports a variety of open-source AI models. We automatically
          recommend models that work best on your system.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Private & Secure</h2>
        <p>
          Your data never leaves your computer. We do not have access to your
          files or models. You are fully in control of your AI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Easy to Use</h2>
        <p>
          No coding required. FennaAI’s interface guides you step by step
          through downloading, training, and chatting with your AI.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Cross-Platform</h2>
        <p>
          FennaAI works on macOS, Windows, and Linux. Mobile and Gmail
          integrations are coming soon.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Regular Updates</h2>
        <p>
          We continually release updates to improve performance, add new models,
          and enhance features. You’ll be notified in-app when updates are
          available.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-item">
        <h2>Community & Support</h2>
        <p>
          Join our user community to share tips, discover model recommendations,
          and get support directly from other FennaAI users.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
      <p>Experience the power of your personal AI. Private. Personal. Yours.</p>
      <button class="download-button">Download FennaAI</button>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
